dct_description_sm: North Decimal Degree 30.433333. South Decimal Degree 30.600000. East Decimal Degree 47.866667. West Decimal Degree 47.633333. Transverse Mercator Projection. Ancillary maps: Southeast Iraq (1:1,500,000). Includes glossary and location map. Standard map series designation: Series K942; "Suitable for reference purposes only." Map shows shipyards, petroleum storage facilities, mined areas. Available also through the Library of Congress website as a raster image http://hdl.loc.gov/loc.gmd/g7614b.ni000004.
dct_publisher_sm: Bethesda, MD : United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency, 2003.
